data.title: Every Wrestler Registered For Fargo (So Far)
data.meta_description: The 2023 US Marine Corps 16U and Junior Nationals are less than a month away. Here's who's registered for Fargo so far.
data.text:
USA Wrestling has started listing team rosters for the US Marine Corps 16U and Junior Nationals. We'll keep track of everyone who's registered for Fargo along with their national rankings. Check this article often as we'll be adding to it almost daily.

State Registration Lists Reported

Alaska, Arkansas, Colorado, Connecticut, Georgia, Indiana, Iowa, Kentucky, Maine, Missouri, Nebraska, Nevada, North Carolina, Ohio, Pennsylvania, South Dakota, Utah, Washington, Wisconsin
